{"kanda":6,"sarga":30,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"ततस्तमक्षोभ्यबलंलङ्काधिपतयेचराः ।सुवेलेराघवंशैलेनिविष्टंप्रत्यवेदयन्","trans":"Thereafter, the spies reported to the king of Lanka that Raghava had camped with an unshakable army at the Suvela mountain.","words":[{"d":"तत","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"चरा","m":"the spies"},{"d":"अक्षोभ्यबलम्","m":"unshakable army"},{"d":"तम्","m":"them"},{"d":"राघवम्","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"सुवेलेशैले","m":"Suvela mountain"},{"d":"निविष्टम्","m":"camped"},{"d":"लङ्काधिपतये","m":"to the king of Lanka"},{"d":"प्रत्यवेदयन्","m":"reported."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"चाराणांरावणश्श्रुत्वाप्राप्तंरामंमहाबलम् ।जातोद्वेगोऽभवत्किञ्चिच्छार्दूलंवाक्यमब्रवीत्","trans":"On hearing from the spies that Rama has camped with a great army, Ravana got a little panicky and said these words to Saardula.","words":[{"d":"रावण","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"महाबलम्","m":"great army"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"Rama"},{"d":"प्राप्तम्","m":"has camped"},{"d":"चाराणाम्","m":"from Spies"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"having heard"},{"d":"किञ्चित्","m":"a little"},{"d":"जातोद्वेग","m":"felt panicky"},{"d":"अभवत्","m":"became"},{"d":"शार्दूलम्","m":"to Saardula"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"अयथावच्चतेवर्णोदीनश्चासिनिशाचर ।नासिकच्चिदमित्राणांक्रुद्धानांवशमागतः","trans":"\"O Forest ranger! Your face is not as it should be and also pitiable. Hope the angry enemies have not done anything to you.\"","words":[{"d":"निशाचर","m":"forest ranger"},{"d":"ते","m":"your"},{"d":"वर्ण","m":"colour (face colour)"},{"d":"आयथावत् च","m":"as it should be"},{"d":"दीनश्च","m":"piteous"},{"d":"अपि","m":"and also"},{"d":"क्रुद्धानाम्","m":"angry"},{"d":"अमित्राणाम्","m":"enemies"},{"d":"वशम्","m":"side"},{"d":"नआगतःकच्चित्","m":"not come to you and done anything."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"इतितेनानुशिष्टस्तुवाचंमन्दमुदीरयत् ।तदाराक्षसशार्दूलंशार्दूलोभयविह्वलः","trans":"And there after questioned by him (Ravana) Saardula revealed these words overwhelmed by fear, in faint tone to the tiger among Rakshasas.","words":[{"d":"इति","m":"and then"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by him"},{"d":"अनुशिष्ट","m":"questioned"},{"d":"भयविह्वल","m":"overwhelmed by fear"},{"d":"शार्दूल","m":"to Saardula"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"राक्षसशार्दूलम्","m":"tiger among Rakshasas"},{"d":"मन्दम्","m":"faint tone"},{"d":"वाचम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"उदीरयत्","m":"revealed."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"नतेचारयितुंशक्याराजन्वानरपुङ्गवाः ।विक्रान्ताबलवन्तश्चराघवेणचरक्षिताः","trans":"\"O King! the Vanara heroes are valiant and highly powerful. They are also protected by Rama. It is not possible to spy on them.\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"O king!"},{"d":"विक्रान्ता","m":"valiant"},{"d":"बलवन्तश्च","m":"highly powerful"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"रक्षिताःच","m":"are protected also"},{"d":"ते","m":"with them"},{"d":"वानरपुङ्गवा","m":"Vanara heroes"},{"d":"चारयितुम्","m":"spy on"},{"d":"नशक्या","m":"not possible."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"नापिसम्भाषितुंशक्यास्सम्प्रश्नोऽत्रनलभ्यते ।सर्वतोरक्ष्यतेपन्थावानरैःपर्वतोपमै","trans":"\"It is not possible to converse with them or to question and or to examine, since they are guarded all over by mountains like Vanaras.\"","words":[{"d":"सम्भाषितुमपि","m":"even to converse"},{"d":"नशक्या","m":"not possible"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"सम्प्रश्न","m":"to question"},{"d":"नविद्यते","m":"not known"},{"d":"पन्था","m":"examine"},{"d":"सर्वत","m":"all over"},{"d":"पर्वतोपमै","m":"resembling mountains"},{"d":"वानरै","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"रक्ष्यते","m":"guarded."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"प्रविष्टमात्रेज्ञातोऽहंबलेतस्मिन्नचारिते ।बलाद्गृहीतोरक्षोभिर्बहुधाऽस्मिविचालितः","trans":"\"No sooner I entered their army, I was detected. I was forcibly seized by their guards and rolled on the ground.\"","words":[{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"their"},{"d":"बले","m":"army"},{"d":"प्रविष्टमात्रे","m":"as soon as I entered into"},{"d":"अचारिते","m":"was observed"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"ज्ञात","m":"was detected"},{"d":"रक्षोभि","m":"even the guards"},{"d":"बलात्","m":"forcibly"},{"d":"गृहीत","m":"seized"},{"d":"बहुधा","m":"many"},{"d":"विचालित","m":"rolled on ground"},{"d":"अस्मि","m":"me."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"जानुभिर्मुष्टिभिर्दन्तेस्तलैश्चाभिहतोभृशम् ।परिणीतोऽस्मिहरिभिर्बलवद्भिरमर्षणैः","trans":"\"The monkeys had beaten me with fists, bitten my palms with teeth, beaten me intensely and paraded me in the army indignantly.\"","words":[{"d":"जानुभि","m":"with knees"},{"d":"मुष्टिभि","m":"with fist"},{"d":"दन्ते","m":"with teeth"},{"d":"तलैश्च","m":"and even with palms"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"intensely"},{"d":"अभिहत","m":"beaten"},{"d":"अमर्षणै","m":"indignantly"},{"d":"हरिभि","m":"the monkeys"},{"d":"बलवद्भि","m":"in the army"},{"d":"परिणीत","m":"paraded"},{"d":"आस्मि","m":"me."}]},{"v":9,"dev":"परिणीयचसर्वत्रनीतोऽहंरामसंसदम् ।रुधिरादिग्धसर्वाङ्गोविह्वलश्चलितेन्द्रियः","trans":"\"With all my limbs wet with bleeding, control over senses lost, after parading, I was led to the assembly of Rama.\"","words":[{"d":"रुधिरादिग्धसर्वाङ्ग","m":"all limbs bleeding"},{"d":"विह्वल","m":"lost senses"},{"d":"चलितेन्द्रिय","m":"lost control of limbs"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"सर्वत्रपरिणीय","m":"all over paraded"},{"d":"रामसंसदम्","m":"to the assembly of Rama"},{"d":"नीत","m":"led."}]},{"v":10,"dev":"हरिभिर्वध्यमानश्चयाचमानःकृताञ्जलिः ।राघवेणपरित्रातोजीवामीतियदृच्छया","trans":"\"While smitten by the monkeys, offering salutation with folded hands, and pleading for protection from Raghava, luckily, I am alive.\"","words":[{"d":"हरिभि","m":"monkeys also"},{"d":"वध्यमान","m":"smitten"},{"d":"कृताञ्जलि","m":"offering salutation with folded palms"},{"d":"याचमान","m":"pleading"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"from Raghava"},{"d":"परित्रात","m":"protection"},{"d":"यदृच्छया","m":"by chance"},{"d":"जीवामीति","m":"alive."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"एषशैलैश्शिलाभिश्चपूरयित्वामहार्णवम् ।द्वारमाश्रित्यलङ्कायारामस्तिष्ठतिसायुधः","trans":"\"Having filled the great ocean with rocks and stones in that way, taking position at the entrance of Lanka Rama stands equipped with arms.\"","words":[{"d":"