र्दूलम्","m":"Saardula"},{"d":"सुमहत्","m":"a good"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"statement"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"uttered."}]},{"v":15,"dev":"यदिमांप्रतियुध्येरन्देवगन्धर्वदानवाः ।नैवसीतांप्रदास्यामिसर्वलोकभयादपि","trans":"\"Even if Devas, Gandharvas and Danavas come to wage war with me and even if I have threats from all worlds, I will not give away Sita.\"","words":[{"d":"यदि","m":"even if"},{"d":"देवगन्धर्वदानव","m":"Devas Gandharvas, Danavas"},{"d":"मांप्रतियुध्येरन","m":"come to wage war with me"},{"d":"सीतां","m":"Sita"},{"d":"प्रदास्यामि","m":"give away"},{"d":"सर्वलोकभयादपि","m":"threat from all worlds"},{"d":"नैव","m":"will not."}]},{"v":16,"dev":"एवमुक्त्वामहातेजारावणःपुनरब्रवीत् ।चरिताभवतासेनाकेऽत्रशूराःप्लवङ्गमाः","trans":"Glorious Ravana having spoken like that, again said (to Saardula), \"You moved about in the army (camp) there. Tell me who among the monkeys are warriors?\"","words":[{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"glorious"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"उक्त्वा","m":"having spoken"},{"d":"पुनः","m":"again"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said"},{"d":"भवता","m":"by you"},{"d":"सेना","m":"army"},{"d":"चरिता","m":"went about"},{"d":"अत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"शूराः","m":"warriors"},{"d":"प्लवङ्गमाः","m":"among the monkeys."}]},{"v":17,"dev":"कीदृशा: किंप्रभा: सौम्यवानरायेदुरासदाः ।कस्यपुत्राश्चपौत्राश्चतत्त्वमाख्याहिराक्षस:।। 6.30.17।।","trans":"\"Gentle Saardula! Of those who are difficult to encounter, what is their description? Who are the powerful ones among them? Whose sons and grandsons, are they? You may speak.\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षस","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"सौम्य","m":"gentle one"},{"d":"दुरासदा","m":"difficult to encounter"},{"d":"ये","m":"those"},{"d":"वानरा","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"किम् प्रभा","m":"who are the powerful ones?"},{"d":"कीदृशा","m":"of what kind कस्य whose"},{"d":"पुत्रा","m":"sons (are they?)"},{"d":"पौत्राश्च","m":"grandsons (are they?)"},{"d":"तत्","m":"it"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"आख्याहि","m":"may speak of."}]},{"v":18